description:
In 2022, InHealth is expanding its services and clinical support in Canada with its first ever sales, customer service, and distribution operation outside the U.S. InHealth Technologies Canada has an exciting opportunity to join our growing team!
We are currently hiring a InHealth Technologies Canada Customer Service Representative who:
works independently with an entrepreneurial spirit and a genuine ability to help customers;
establishes trust with customers by responding promptly to inquiries related to products, product shipments, and invoices.
is self-motivated and thrives in a fast –paced, remote location, work environment;

